label: BTZEUMV1
info_overview: The universal module enables the control of existing electrical locking systems via smartphone. It is a circuit board with a relay to switch potential-free contacts. The module is connected near the lock system and actuates engine locks, garage doors, digital cylinders or the door number.
info_inclusion:
To add or include the Danalock into a Z-Wave network

  1. Set the controller in inclusion mode
  2. Push the switch once until you hear two beeps.
info_exclusion:
To remove or exclude the Danalock from a Z-Wave network

  1. Set the controller in inclusion mode
  2. Push the switch once until you hear two beeps.
